      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bfedb6e06.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6beddb0736.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bee13d5f5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bee4941e4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bee820b38.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6beed463b0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bf5ed8c90.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bf64903b0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bf6725adc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fc6bf69cc07a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Standalone version&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a petition, I added the mod as a standalone too. Install it and check the Akkala Ancient Lab.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreyColor"&gt;Please note it's a very basic port with the bare minimum (icon, model, text, physics).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This small mod is a request, and it replaces the default&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Ruby Circlet&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;with the Linkle short haircut and the ruby earrings found in my&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/167663"&gt;Linkle Snowquill replacement&lt;/a&gt; mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can also install it as standalone, purchasable at Akkala Ancient Lab. Just choose the appropriate mod file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please note on the initial version of the mod, the hair had a different light reflection compared with the hairstyle in the &lt;i&gt;Snowquill&lt;/i&gt; mod. This has been finally addressed on version 2.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank" class="SelectedElement"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;The makeup Linkle is using in the pictures is not included in this mod, but you can get it&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/skins/181455"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
