      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Sep 2025 18:49:52 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6228b76706728.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6228b76709ff0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6228b76713037.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6228b76732cb9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68d03ac0daa6a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Update 21.09.2025&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: mnemonic fix (lwzxu-&gt;lwzux)&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: additional item drop settings&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Optimization&lt;/em&gt;: item glitter animation removed&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: minor adjustment of some actor parameters&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: 'red potion system' support&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Materials not stored in the inventory and used for modded game mechanics (normal rupees still works)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PREREQUISITES&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;- &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/gamefiles/19908"&gt;Data Layer&lt;/a&gt; (last version)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;- &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49876"&gt;Durability UI&lt;/a&gt; (last version)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;NOTES&lt;br&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr align="center"&gt;&lt;td&gt;Fake rupees&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Details&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Modded game mechanics&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr valign="middle"&gt;&lt;td align="center"&gt;Ancient Crystal&lt;br&gt;(PutAncientCrystal)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;• +5 (-1*BombsNum.MinValue) bombs&lt;br&gt;• RupeeValue: 0xB08&lt;br&gt;• Dropped by guardians, Yiga footsoldiers, wooden boxes and 3 treasure chests&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;• Remote bomb rune as bomb bag&lt;br&gt;• -1 bomb when bomb ready even if it not used afterwards&lt;br&gt;• Experimental option to disable the wind bomb&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr valign="middle"&gt;&lt;td align="center"&gt;Red Potion&lt;br&gt;(PutRedPotion)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;• restores 12 pieces of heart&lt;br&gt;• RupeeValue: 12&lt;br&gt;• Dropped by Yiga Blademasters, hinoxes, lynels, treasure Octoroks, barrels and pots&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Healing potion system found in several Zelda games&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="3"&gt;[Some quick ideas maybe for the future]&lt;br&gt;Feather for Revali's Gale&lt;br&gt;Blessed Screw, Gear of the Protector, Benevolent Spring as basic materials to get fake rupee for stasis&lt;br&gt;Cursed Bone Shard, Malevolent Spine, Heart of Annihilation as basic materials to get fake rupee for magnesis&lt;br&gt;...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br&gt;INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS&lt;br&gt;- browse to your Cemu folder&lt;br&gt;- open the &lt;i&gt;graphicPacks&lt;/i&gt; folder&lt;br&gt;- store the &lt;i&gt;BreathOfTheWild_FakeRupees&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;BreathOfTheWild_BombBag&lt;/i&gt; folders in this directory&lt;br&gt;- enable the &lt;i&gt;Fake Rupees&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;Bomb Bag&lt;/i&gt; graphic packs in Cemu&lt;br&gt;- install &lt;i&gt;BreathOfTheWild_AncientCrystal.bnp&lt;/i&gt; with BCML (pay attention to conflicts with other mods using custom drop tables)&lt;br&gt;- install &lt;i&gt;BreathOfTheWild_RedPotion.bnp&lt;/i&gt; with BCML (pay attention to conflicts with other mods using custom drop tables)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;DONATIONS (only if you have too many rupees)&lt;br&gt;Donate to &lt;a href="https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=5CWWWZPQUUPQ8¤cy_code=EUR" target="_blank"&gt;dragbe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Donate to the &lt;a href="https://www.patreon.com/cemu" target="_blank"&gt;Cemu team&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Donate to &lt;a href="https://www.patreon.com/nicenenerdbcml" target="_blank"&gt;NiceneNerd&lt;/a&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/breathofthewild_fakerupees_0fb19.zip" type="application/zip"/>
