    <item>
      <title>BOTW Mousecam</title>
      <author>mcrib884</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/619327</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/619327#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">574e9ff5da0a32a6628a28dd5e7a327b30d34415</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 23:06:57 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68c2048b83153.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68c2048c968bf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mouse controlled camera mod for Botw.Works by overriding the game camera using dll injection and memory editing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;How to install:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Extract the "injector.exe,position_finder.exe and botw-mousecam.dll" files into the same folder as cemu.exe&lt;br&gt;Once you are in-game,launch the mod using injector.exe,adjust the confgiurations,bind the same keys you use in cemu input settings accordingly.once you are done,press c  and enter to close the menu,and press F3 to enable the mod.enjoy!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you encounter any bugs,which you most likely will,you can temporarily close the mod until the problem goes away.Unfortunately i don't think i'll be able to make the mod more advanced than this.so as long as the bug is not something i havent thought of,or havent encountered yet,it won't get fixed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Changelog 1.1&lt;br&gt;*Added sprint toggle feature&lt;br&gt;*Fixed some localizations&lt;br&gt;*Fixed link getting invisible randomly.&lt;br&gt;Changelog 1.2:&lt;br&gt; Added fps magnesis mode &lt;br&gt; Fixed the twitchy zoom with mousewheel&lt;br&gt;What works:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-in game camera&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-aiming camera&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-sheikah slate camera&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-magnesis&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What doesnt work:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-collision detection (gotta zoom in manually by mousewheel)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-magnesis item isnt always rotated,and is not very good with high speeds.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-sometimes the camera might freak out,or the mod may stop working.if disabling and re enabling with f3 wont fix it,then save and load the game it should start working again.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;made by mcrib884,thanks to the works of etra0 and LibreVR.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you wanna support me,you can do so by donating to an organization for children.preferably for palestinian children.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Note: This mod uses DLL injection to work. Because DLL injectors use the same techniques as cheats and malware, Windows Defender or other antivirus software may flag the injector EXE as suspicious. This is a false positive. If you’re uncomfortable, you can build the injector yourself from the provided source code&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;source code:https://github.com/mcrib884/botw-mousecam</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/release_12_af0c6.zip" type="application/zip"/>
