ons! This pack includes ALL previous releases as well as updates to them!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;The above image are &lt;u&gt;ONLY SOME&lt;/u&gt; of the new outfits added. With everything together,  the amount of content totals to a WHOPPING 6 PAGES of armors. SEE FOR YOURSELF WHAT ELSE HAS BEEN ADDED!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Notable updates:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;- SilverVale set has the tail as part of the head armor component allowing you to use other torso and leg armors as silvervale. This was done with the added Cat Set too.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Vai Sets has Thiccer Thighs/ass&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Zora has Thiccer Thighs/ass&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cow Nude Thighs/ass uses the new sexy bubble shape&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Both Vai sets have a alternative version that uses a bigger bubble shaped ass and a low cut top &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;AND ARE DYEABLE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Basic small nude uses a new top and bottom shape&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Swimsuit Silvervale now has a new hairstyle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mannequin has a bigger ass lol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Extra: &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;This download includes a small